1
00:00:06,060 --> 00:00:08,340
♪The white sail came too late♪

2
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:11,340
♪Where did he go?♪

3
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:13,820
♪Snow veils the mountains♪

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:16,340
♪Love endures beyond life and death♪

5
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:19,580
♪A black chess piece♪

6
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:23,140
♪Whose game did he stumble into?♪

7
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:27,620
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

8
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:33,340
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

9
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:40,020
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

10
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:42,620
♪I will remember♪

11
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:46,660
♪Those days long past♪

12
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:51,580
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

13
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,660
♪Ten thousand years ago♪

14
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:57,500
♪Did you once walk this shore?♪

15
00:00:57,740 --> 00:01:02,940
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

16
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,100
♪I am lost yet willing♪

17
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:09,580
♪Still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

18
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:17,100
♪Until all things fade away♪

19
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,220
♪The stars will remember us♪

20
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,220
[Love & Crown]

21
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from the novel "My Queen" by Xie Lounan]

22
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 12]

23
00:01:33,230 --> 00:01:34,900
Grand Tutor Ling forced me to choose.

24
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,570
So, I want him to know

25
00:01:36,870 --> 00:01:38,210
how hard that choice is.

26
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,390
I'm innocent!

27
00:01:42,050 --> 00:01:42,720
Your Majesty,

28
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:44,660
I'm truly innocent!

29
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:47,100
I never forced Your Majesty!

30
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,260
Father...

31
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,740
Sir,

32
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,180
I want to save the people of Jiangzhou

33
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,260
and the people of Xuzhou.

34
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,540
Tell me,

35
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,100
what should I do?

36
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:07,490
If you're killing me, do it.

37
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:08,670
No need for all this chatter!

38
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,500
Loose the arrows!

39
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,730
No!

40
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,220
[Wine]

41
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,060
No!

42
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,610
Your Majesty...

43
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,100
I'm begging you!

44
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:33,890
Please let him go!

45
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,690
It was my fault!

46
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,980
Please, Your Majesty!

47
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,890
Just let him go...

48
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,980
I'm begging you...

49
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:45,170
I was wrong...

50
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,730
It's all my fault...

51
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:54,980
Please...

52
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,730
Sir,

53
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,340
what do you say?

54
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,720
I will

55
00:03:03,210 --> 00:03:04,790
do everything I can

56
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:08,850
to get grain to Xuzhou and Jiangzhou.

57
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:10,170
I was wrong!

58
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,980
It's all my fault!

59
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,410
Xiao Huan...

60
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,100
Xiao Huan...

61
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,730
spare him...

62
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:22,610
Please spare him, I'm begging you...

63
00:03:30,780 --> 00:03:32,740
[Wine]

64
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,130
Cangcang.

65
00:03:40,850 --> 00:03:41,400
Father.

66
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:46,690
My death means nothing!

67
00:03:47,310 --> 00:03:48,260
I only hope

68
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:50,690
you're never threatened again!

69
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,130
Luo!

70
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:12,010
No!

71
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,410
Luo!

72
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:21,820
♪The rouge spilling into old snow♪

73
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:24,660
♪The waning moon in your eyes♪

74
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:27,660
♪Is the flaw of half my life♪

75
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:33,980
♪Oaths wither at the root of the tongue♪

76
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:40,340
♪Only a wisp of smoke binds the butterfly♪

77
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:43,580
♪The blood on my hairpin is my hatred♪

78
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:46,940
♪The layer of melted candle wax is my love♪

79
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:49,700
♪Only blind devotion♪

80
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:54,020
♪Can warm this heartless night♪

81
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:55,820
♪You and I...♪

82
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,980
Xianxue...

83
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,730
Cangcang...

84
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,740
♪Using the sweetest curse...♪

85
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,610
I can't protect you anymore.

86
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,370
You have to live well.

87
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,100
You must keep on living!

88
00:05:15,460 --> 00:05:16,740
♪We brew our hottest tears♪

89
00:05:17,060 --> 00:05:18,540
♪Into the deadliest wine♪

90
00:05:18,700 --> 00:05:20,700
♪And fall drunk at midnight, caught between dream and reality♪

91
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:22,740
♪Later I heard♪

92
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:26,020
♪You once asked where I'd gone♪

93
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:32,180
♪But the Buddha says this world was a mistake♪

94
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,100
Still trying to run?

95
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:21,980
Let me tell you:

96
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:23,940
Even if you flee to the ends of the earth,

97
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:25,900
with this Heartbane in you,

98
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,370
there's no escape!

99
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,490
I...

100
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,220
I won't dare again.

101
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:32,020
Never again.

102
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:36,700
You opened this Butterfly Lock?

103
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,700
Yes.

104
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,850
Such a complicated Butterfly Lock,

105
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,490
and you still managed to open it.

106
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,850
Looks like you've got some skills.

107
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,050
Come with me.

108
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,140
I have a disciple

109
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:51,610
named Cangcang.

110
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:54,660
You'll stay by her side,

111
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:56,020
and be her friend.

112
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:59,250
No matter what happens,

113
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,730
you must protect her,

114
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:02,850
even if it costs your life.

115
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,410
Cangcang,

116
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,250
why don't we go back to Southern Chu

117
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,490
and rebuild Fenglai Pavilion?

118
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:11,250
Can I ever be the Ling Cangcang I used to be?

119
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:21,620
[Pure and Spotless]

120
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:25,340
Greetings, Your Majesty.

121
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,410
Grand Tutor Ling, you're in quite a hurry.

122
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:29,540
Is there news of the grain?

123
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,540
Your Majesty,

124
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,020
I've contacted the grain merchants

125
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,050
in the Capital and all the prefectures.

126
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:36,900
They've volunteered 300 thousand dan of grain.

127
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:39,020
It'll all be delivered within a month.

128
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,540
This is their joint petition.

129
00:07:58,630 --> 00:07:59,410
Eunuch Feng,

130
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,540
show Grand Tutor Ling the plan

131
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,700
to send aid to Jiangzhou.

132
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,780
Yes, Your Majesty.

133
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,580
Your Majesty.

134
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,780
What's the matter?

135
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,370
We truly cannot go back?

136
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,980
From the very beginning,

137
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,300
there was only deceit between us.

138
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,460
My death means nothing!

139
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,010
I only hope

140
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,820
you're never threatened again!

141
00:08:55,140 --> 00:08:56,900
♪The wild geese cry long♪

142
00:08:57,700 --> 00:09:01,140
♪Tonight my homeland feels as distant as a foreign shore...♪

143
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:05,220
Why did you kill my master?

144
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:07,850
Did you approach me

145
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:13,530
just to kill my master?

146
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:16,610
I know you misunderstood me before.

147
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,340
Can you give me one more chance

148
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,130
so we can start over?

149
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:23,420
♪Pale moonlight♪

150
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:25,740
♪Burns the stars for you♪

151
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:28,020
♪Drifting far...♪

152
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,650
You don't need to rush to answer me.

153
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,220
I'll stay by your side

154
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,340
until you willingly walk toward me.

155
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,180
This is the palace,

156
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,700
not the martial world.

157
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:44,180
The palace is an arena of power,

158
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:46,530
not a place that cares about right or wrong.

159
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,940
Ling Cangcang,

160
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,530
you're still not ruthless enough.

161
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:54,900
♪A few strands of warmth still remain...♪

162
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,340
Cangcang,

163
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,850
what are you doing?

164
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,580
It's so quiet here.

165
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,460
I'm just calming down here

166
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:22,770
and thinking some things through.

167
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:25,700
Think about what?

168
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,100
First,

169
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,220
you used me again,

170
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:34,100
killing two birds with one stone.

171
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,530
You forced my father to give in

172
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,770
and got Luo killed.

173
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:47,820
I never once thought of using you,

174
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,850
and I never meant

175
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,580
to drive Luo Xianxue to his death.

176
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,580
It doesn't matter anymore.

177
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,180
He's gone for good, anyway.

178
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:00,420
Second,

179
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,530
I don't want to be empress

180
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,340
not even for one more day.

181
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,100
This splendid capital

182
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:14,580
is rotten with schemes and treachery.

183
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:17,130
I used to think

184
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,650
that staying in this palace, I could at least protect

185
00:11:19,670 --> 00:11:21,010
the people I care about.

186
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,940
I lost.

187
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,060
And I'm tired.

188
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:33,260
♪A few strokes of history's ink...♪

189
00:11:37,750 --> 00:11:40,100
Tell me, if I really jump from here,

190
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,030
will I finally be free?

191
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,010
There's one more thing.

192
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:53,650
Do you want to hear it?

193
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,460
What?

194
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:59,380
♪Shot at the moonlight?♪

195
00:12:01,540 --> 00:12:03,900
♪Singing to the boundless sky...♪

196
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:06,730
I hate myself for judging people so poorly,

197
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:09,180
for giving my heart to the wrong person.

198
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:13,370
I deserve this heartbreak.

199
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:21,370
Zhong Lin.

200
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,460
Zhong Lin...

201
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:40,340
What are you hiding?

202
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,700
Nothing. I was just carving.

203
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,580
Oh, right...

204
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,130
I just went to see the Empress.

205
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:47,580
Do you know what she said to me?

206
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:48,420
What did she say?

207
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:54,490
You've got guts, Zhong Lin.

208
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:57,250
Now you even dare forge the Imperial Seal!

209
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:01,740
[Palace Defense Map]

210
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:04,100
A map of the palace defenses?

211
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:06,340
Zhong Lin, are you insane?

212
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,700
Do you know what you're doing?

213
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,460
Keep your voice down!

214
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,370
Are you trying to get me killed?

215
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,890
I'm getting you killed?

216
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:15,490
Right in my manor,

217
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,490
you're making something like this.

218
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:17,820
You're trying to get me killed!

219
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,770
This is a capital crime that wipes out your whole clan!

220
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:21,940
I don't even have a clan.

221
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,700
Besides,

222
00:13:24,750 --> 00:13:26,250
if you keep quiet, who'll ever know?

223
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,060
Move. You're blocking my light.

224
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,770
What exactly are you trying to do?

225
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:43,100
I'm going to save Cangcang.

226
00:13:43,550 --> 00:13:45,770
Abducting the Empress is a capital crime too.

227
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,060
Trust you to come up with that!

228
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,370
Cangcang sent me a message.

229
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:51,060
She said she doesn't want to stay in the palace.

230
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,490
Anything Cangcang wants to do,

231
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:55,340
I have to help her do it.

232
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,820
Your plan definitely won't work.

233
00:13:58,630 --> 00:14:00,490
Then do you have a better one?

234
00:14:03,030 --> 00:14:04,850
I'm the Prince of Yuzhang.

235
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:07,130
What's wrong with me taking someone out?

236
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,010
So can you help me?

237
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,530
As long as you help me,

238
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,300
I can...

239
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,420
You can...

240
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,730
do what?

241
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,980
I can help you take Xiao Huan's throne.

242
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:29,890
I'll risk life and limb,

243
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:30,820
whatever it takes!

244
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:36,100
You hate Xiao Huan that much?

245
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:40,180
If he makes Cangcang sad,

246
00:14:40,270 --> 00:14:41,580
then I'm not okay with it.

247
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:43,730
Anyone Cangcang doesn't like,

248
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:44,850
I don't like either.

249
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,980
So are you helping me or not?

250
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:04,370
Depends on my mood.

251
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,250
Depends on your mood?

252
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:12,850
So that's a no!

253
00:15:14,980 --> 00:15:18,900
[Linghe Hall]

254
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:33,300
Your Majesty.

255
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:36,180
This was sent over from Xuanguang Hall.

256
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,770
It looks like wine mash,

257
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,610
but why is it shaped so oddly?

258
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:50,850
You may go.

259
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:52,180
Yes, Your Majesty.

260
00:16:17,980 --> 00:16:19,860
[Token]

261
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:34,530
His Majesty arrives!

262
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,220
Greetings, Your Majesty.

263
00:16:53,630 --> 00:16:54,530
Three days from now,

264
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:56,530
the reinforcements will depart for Jiangzhou

265
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:58,010
to support General Ling.

266
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:02,890
Thank you, Your Majesty.

267
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,730
As for Luo Xianxue's death,

268
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,570
I never expected

269
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:13,980
he would do that.

270
00:17:15,530 --> 00:17:16,150
I understand.

271
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,810
Your Majesty has your own burdens.

272
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,220
You need not blame yourself.

273
00:17:25,830 --> 00:17:26,620
Cangcang,

274
00:17:26,830 --> 00:17:27,900
you've gotten much thinner lately...

275
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:41,570
Your Majesty,

276
00:17:42,830 --> 00:17:43,730
I heard

277
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:45,050
when the reinforcements march out,

278
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,730
Nanrong Palace will hold a grand river-offering ceremony

279
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:49,050
at the banks of the Qining River,

280
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:50,490
praying for the soldiers.

281
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:51,330
Is that so?

282
00:17:52,550 --> 00:17:53,220
Yes.

283
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,620
Would you care to attend with me?

284
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:01,050
I was actually going to say

285
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,180
I'm not fond of noisy occasions,

286
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:05,570
so I won't go.

287
00:18:34,510 --> 00:18:36,770
His Majesty arrives!

288
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:41,530
Greetings, Your Majesty.

289
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:47,570
Carry on with your drills.

290
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,010
How are preparations

291
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:54,180
for the ceremony coming along?

292
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,010
Please rest assured.

293
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:57,770
Everything is ready.

294
00:18:58,070 --> 00:19:00,490
As for the finale of the fireworks,

295
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,220
would you prefer a golden dragon in the sky,

296
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,420
or...?

297
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:06,940
A golden phoenix.

298
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:08,460
Let the golden phoenix see them off

299
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,050
and bless their journey.

300
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:12,180
The Empress doesn't even want to come.

301
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:14,460
Does it really mean anything

302
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,420
to do all this?

303
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,290
What if

304
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:22,010
the Empress

305
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,050
changes her mind?

306
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:40,010
She doesn't have you in her heart.

307
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:42,250
Why would she change her mind?

308
00:19:51,550 --> 00:19:54,180
Did you get the exit token I sent you?

309
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,180
In two days,

310
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:03,050
it's the river-offering ceremony.

311
00:20:03,310 --> 00:20:05,420
With crowds going in and out of the palace,

312
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:06,810
that token

313
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:09,180
will let you leave.

314
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,330
Why are you helping me?

315
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,180
I gave Zhong Lin my word.

316
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:17,700
More than helping Zhong Lin,

317
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:20,180
I'm afraid what you want most is to see

318
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,420
the Emperor and Empress fall out.

319
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,010
You saw through all that?

320
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,330
If you leave my brother,

321
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:29,010
the Ling clan won't be backing him as much.

322
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:30,810
Then,

323
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,770
I'll have my chance.

324
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,490
Thank you for your kindness,

325
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,290
but I have my own way.

326
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:41,700
You really don't need my help?

327
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:44,770
I'm usually cold and heartless.

328
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:46,570
It's rare I offer to help.

329
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:48,180
And you

330
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,730
still don't appreciate it?

331
00:20:54,750 --> 00:20:56,530
I don't want Zhong Lin owing you a favor.

332
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:58,460
There's one more thing

333
00:20:58,920 --> 00:20:59,900
I'd like to ask of you.

334
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:01,770
Go ahead.

335
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,420
Please take good care of Zhong Lin.

336
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:05,980
Don't let her come looking for me.

337
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,490
Where are you going?

338
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,290
Better if you don't know.

339
00:21:23,590 --> 00:21:24,330
Ladies,

340
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:26,730
this year's river-offering ceremony is especially grand.

341
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:29,530
I hear His Majesty will personally see off the troops.

342
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:31,810
I heard that too.

343
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:34,140
To be chosen by Preceptor Du to dance

344
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,620
is such an honor.

345
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,380
Yeah.

346
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,570
After today's sword dance,

347
00:21:37,590 --> 00:21:39,050
we get to escort the army out of the city.

348
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:40,180
How glorious is that!

349
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:40,860
Yeah!

350
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:43,330
Ladies!

351
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:44,810
Ladies,

352
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,810
the river-offering ceremony is about to begin.

353
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:48,810
Hurry and come with me.

354
00:21:48,990 --> 00:21:50,050
- Move it! - Come on, quickly!

355
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,700
[Qi]

356
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:28,980
Her Majesty still refuses to come.

357
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:46,420
Our best wishes to His Majesty and the Empress Dowager!

358
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:51,730
Rise!

359
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:03,050
The Empress still hasn't changed her mind.

360
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:06,460
To skip such an important ceremony,

361
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,660
seems she has no respect

362
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:12,530
for our ancestral rites.

363
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:14,420
The Empress cares deeply for Great Qi.

364
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,530
Wherever she is,

365
00:23:16,550 --> 00:23:18,290
she'll be praying for our land.

366
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:22,140
Let's begin!

367
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,010
Yes, Your Majesty.

368
00:23:30,350 --> 00:23:34,330
The auspicious hour has come!

369
00:23:40,270 --> 00:23:41,730
We, the people of Great Qi,

370
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,700
[Tablet of the River Deity]
with heaven, earth, sun and moon as our bounds,

371
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,620
and nourished by the grace of our rivers,

372
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:47,220
rise early and toil till night,

373
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,570
plowing fields and tending grain.

374
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,860
We pray the River Deity to bless Great Qi,

375
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,140
let our lands be rich,

376
00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:53,490
our harvests be full,

377
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:55,050
winds and rains be gentle,

378
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:56,570
and our years full of plenty.

379
00:24:00,750 --> 00:24:02,980
Offer incense!

380
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:23,380
Offer the wine!

381
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:37,220
Send the offerings!

382
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:42,330
Sword dance to honor Heaven,

383
00:24:42,510 --> 00:24:43,810
may our land stand strong!

384
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:01,940
Today's sword dance was well done.

385
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:03,620
All of you, step forward.

386
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:32,620
I like your dance very much.

387
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:33,730
Today,

388
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:35,940
you'll join me for the banner rite.

389
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:36,700
Your Majesty,

390
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:38,330
this goes against ritual.

391
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,700
In the Emperor's banner rite,

392
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:41,290
how can a mere palace maid stand beside you?

393
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:43,420
I've already decided.

394
00:26:43,550 --> 00:26:44,900
No need to say more.

395
00:26:45,750 --> 00:26:46,530
I

396
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:49,180
just want to stand with you.

397
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,570
His Majesty shoots the banner

398
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:09,980
to honor the river!

399
00:27:16,380 --> 00:27:21,700
♪The rouge spilling into old snow♪

400
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:24,980
♪The waning moon in your eyes♪

401
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:27,980
♪Is the flaw of half my life♪

402
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:34,460
♪Oaths wither at the root of the tongue♪

403
00:27:35,620 --> 00:27:40,820
♪Only a wisp of smoke binds the butterfly♪

404
00:27:41,620 --> 00:27:44,060
♪The blood on my hairpin is my hatred...♪

405
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:47,940
Today, I offer sacrifice to the deity

406
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:50,010
to bless the soldiers of Great Qi.

407
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:51,460
May you keep our land safe

408
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:52,700
and return in triumph!

409
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:59,770
- Return in triumph! - Return in triumph!

410
00:27:59,940 --> 00:28:02,940
♪And to share the red kiss of a blade upon the neck♪

411
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:04,260
♪We brew our hottest tears♪

412
00:28:04,620 --> 00:28:06,020
♪Into the deadliest wine...♪

413
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:07,220
Did you plan

414
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:09,180
to give me a surprise?

415
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:16,700
Let me go.

416
00:28:20,500 --> 00:28:22,780
♪The empty pouch you gave♪

417
00:28:22,860 --> 00:28:25,260
♪Is filled with my grief...♪

418
00:28:25,700 --> 00:28:26,850
Is life by my side

419
00:28:27,260 --> 00:28:28,780
really worse than death?

420
00:28:35,270 --> 00:28:36,050
It is.

421
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:41,100
♪So much for vows of growing old together♪

422
00:28:41,180 --> 00:28:45,620
♪Whatever fancy promises have been reduced to ashes...♪

423
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:46,460
All right.

424
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:48,220
You may go.

425
00:28:48,220 --> 00:28:50,820
♪Hugging across from the magpie bridge and the galaxy♪

426
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:53,820
♪Shattering glazed fantasy with these sewn shoes♪

427
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:55,500
♪Using the sweetest curse♪

428
00:28:55,660 --> 00:28:57,140
♪To build the coldest graveyard♪

429
00:28:57,260 --> 00:29:00,420
♪Buried under the parasol tree during the sorrowful night rain♪

430
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:03,620
♪Are destined to meet on that autumn day of White Dew♪

431
00:29:03,940 --> 00:29:06,580
♪And to share the red kiss of a blade upon the neck♪

432
00:29:06,900 --> 00:29:08,180
♪We brew our hottest tears♪

433
00:29:08,500 --> 00:29:09,980
♪Into the deadliest wine♪

434
00:29:10,140 --> 00:29:12,260
♪And fall drunk at midnight, caught between dream and reality♪

435
00:29:12,260 --> 00:29:14,100
♪Later I heard♪

436
00:29:14,220 --> 00:29:17,340
♪You once asked where I'd gone♪

437
00:29:17,980 --> 00:29:22,660
♪But the Buddha says this world was a mistake♪

438
00:29:27,790 --> 00:29:28,940
I always thought

439
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:31,730
Your Majesty would never show your emotions.

440
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:33,660
Turns out

441
00:29:34,350 --> 00:29:36,290
you just hadn't met the one you cared about.

442
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:38,380
That palace maid today

443
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:39,730
was the Empress.

444
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:43,940
Since you recognized her,

445
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:45,940
why let her go?

446
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,900
You've done so much for her,

447
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,490
and she knows nothing.

448
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,770
Letting her walk away like this,

449
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:57,660
can you really accept that?

450
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:01,290
What she wants is freedom.

451
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:03,250
In your whole life,

452
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:05,700
have you ever had a single moment of freedom?

453
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:09,010
I never had a choice.

454
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:11,250
That's why

455
00:30:12,350 --> 00:30:13,980
I don't want her to become another me.

456
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:38,620
♪Dust gathers on the lost paths of time♪

457
00:30:41,940 --> 00:30:46,740
♪A red candle keeps the dusk company in solitude...♪

458
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:48,490
You want to go to Jiangzhou, don't you?

459
00:30:52,350 --> 00:30:53,180
You may go.

460
00:30:53,260 --> 00:30:57,340
♪Broken speech in twisted time♪

461
00:30:57,540 --> 00:30:59,340
♪The heart still hums♪

462
00:30:59,340 --> 00:31:03,060
♪Its old song of longing♪

463
00:31:04,580 --> 00:31:05,740
♪On Phoenix Terrace...♪

464
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:08,420
From Phoenix Terrace I gaze at the sky.

465
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:11,770
Only the golden phoenix carries parting in its wings.

466
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,050
Phoenix and fenghuang

467
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,940
were meant to fly together.

468
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,420
If only the golden phoenix flies alone,

469
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:24,660
isn't that the saddest farewell of all?

470
00:31:27,260 --> 00:31:28,820
♪Oh, broken-hearted one♪

471
00:31:28,940 --> 00:31:34,140
♪Still you wander the world♪

472
00:31:42,860 --> 00:31:45,740
[Linghe Hall]

473
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:52,620
[Fate's rise and fall heed no one's will]

474
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:32,140
[Fate's rise and fall heed no one's will]

475
00:32:35,550 --> 00:32:36,530
Rise.

476
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,330
From today on,

477
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,490
the Empress will be said to suffer from head pains

478
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:42,860
and will recover in the outer palace.

479
00:32:43,310 --> 00:32:44,290
No one

480
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:45,660
is allowed an audience.

481
00:33:36,750 --> 00:33:38,460
You truly love her that much?

482
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:50,770
Ling Cangcang,

483
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,810
you've hurt him this deeply.

484
00:33:55,550 --> 00:33:57,180
If you stir up trouble again,

485
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:00,460
I will never let you live in peace!

486
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,130
Your Majesty.

487
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,690
Give this Phoenix Seal

488
00:34:24,110 --> 00:34:25,130
to Cangcang for me.

489
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:26,340
Your Majesty...

490
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,940
She is Empress of Great Qi after all.

491
00:34:29,070 --> 00:34:30,260
Whether she accepts it or not,

492
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:31,690
this Phoenix Seal

493
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,210
belongs to her.

494
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:34,170
Yes, Your Majesty.

495
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:50,340
Cangcang...

496
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,010
I let you go.

497
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,940
May you one day truly be free.

498
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:58,900
♪In the distance♪

499
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:02,980
♪A lone lamp glows♪

500
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:07,740
♪That light♪

501
00:35:09,140 --> 00:35:13,380
♪Was never mine to claim...♪

502
00:35:17,070 --> 00:35:17,860
Speak.

503
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:18,570
What is it?

504
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:22,340
His Majesty ordered me

505
00:35:22,550 --> 00:35:24,050
to bring you the Phoenix Seal

506
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:25,780
and say you will always be Empress of Great Qi.

507
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,570
Have you ever seen an empress who walked away from the palace?

508
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:32,020
♪Gently to the night sky

509
00:35:33,700 --> 00:35:38,100
♪Raindrops fall with the wind♪

510
00:35:38,300 --> 00:35:42,860
♪Caressing the mountains' scars♪

511
00:35:44,260 --> 00:35:47,380
♪Like someone both strange and dear♪

512
00:35:47,380 --> 00:35:48,060
[Pure and Spotless]

513
00:35:48,060 --> 00:35:52,180
♪Whispering love and hate♪

514
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:57,020
♪How many past tales stained red?♪

515
00:35:57,340 --> 00:36:02,940
♪I'm swept into the endless torrent...♪

516
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,130
Your Majesty,

517
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:05,780
it's time for your medicine.

518
00:36:06,510 --> 00:36:07,460
Leave it there for now.

519
00:36:10,110 --> 00:36:11,170
The situation at the front is complicated.

520
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:13,490
There's no need to press yourself.

521
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,650
Please take care of your health.

522
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,340
I know what I'm doing.

523
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:19,690
You may go.

524
00:36:31,540 --> 00:36:33,940
♪Falling petals♪

525
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:38,020
♪Petals drifting through the sky...♪

526
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:41,530
Your Majesty.

527
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:45,860
Is she all right?

528
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:48,610
The Empress slipped into the westbound relief army.

529
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:49,490
She's fine for now.

530
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:52,170
Once the battle reports from Jiangzhou arrive,

531
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:53,980
bring them straight to me.

532
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:54,740
Yes, Your Majesty.

533
00:36:55,420 --> 00:36:59,300
♪That watchful waiting once warmed a whole city...♪

534
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:02,260
You let her go,

535
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:04,860
yet you still can't let her go.

536
00:37:08,620 --> 00:37:13,020
♪Raindrops fall with the wind♪

537
00:37:13,220 --> 00:37:17,780
♪Caressing the mountains' scars♪

538
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:22,300
♪Like someone both strange and dear♪

539
00:37:22,980 --> 00:37:27,100
♪Whispering love and hate♪

540
00:37:27,540 --> 00:37:31,940
♪Raindrops drift along the wind♪

541
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:37,860
♪You fall into my desolate heart♪

542
00:37:38,220 --> 00:37:41,220
♪Silently, they pierce through♪

543
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:45,140
♪The wounds time has left behind♪

544
00:38:05,180 --> 00:38:07,740
♪Dawn breaks♪

545
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:09,140
♪After a night of storm♪

546
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:10,340
♪Petals carpet the ground♪

547
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:13,100
♪All cause, all consequence♪

548
00:38:14,900 --> 00:38:17,260
♪Dawn sinks into hush♪

549
00:38:17,620 --> 00:38:18,740
[Wuying Hall]
♪The flood runs on to the sea♪

550
00:38:18,860 --> 00:38:19,900
♪Fate dies, then blooms again♪

551
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:23,140
♪Through loss and gain, it goes on♪

552
00:38:26,980 --> 00:38:31,380
♪How many memories lost to time?♪

553
00:38:31,580 --> 00:38:36,580
♪I remain in the endless torrent♪

554
00:38:37,540 --> 00:38:41,220
♪Drifting with the river into silent seas♪

555
00:38:41,700 --> 00:38:49,780
♪As dawn darkens the distant peaks♪

556
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:53,900
[Wuying Hall]

557
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:55,380
Your Majesty,

558
00:38:55,630 --> 00:38:58,780
the westbound reinforcements will reach Jiangzhou tomorrow.

559
00:38:59,070 --> 00:39:02,300
You can finally get a proper sleep.

560
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,090
Hand me the map.

561
00:39:04,670 --> 00:39:05,460
Yes, Your Majesty.

562
00:39:24,940 --> 00:39:28,780
[Jiangzhou]

563
00:39:32,460 --> 00:39:34,060
[Jiangzhou]

564
00:40:11,590 --> 00:40:12,740
One hard push,

565
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:15,340
[Kumor, King of Xijiang]
take this city today!

